query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS bot_instance_lock (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT 1,
  instanceId VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  lockedAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  expiresAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  CHECK (id = 1)
)
